{"type":"message","id":"94bab533","parentId":"c8494f2f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T19:47:38.882Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Thu 2026-05-21 03:47 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 修改 ISAPI 代理，自动从 credentials API 获取凭证：\n\n文件：D:\\astro_py\\astro_hub\\src\\main\\main.py\n\n找到 `_handle_isapi_request` 函数，修改：\n\n当前逻辑：\n```python\ndevice = _isapi_devices.get(device_ip, {'username': 'admin', 'password': 'Nftw1357', 'port': device_port})\n```\n\n改为：\n```python\n# Get credentials: first check _isapi_devices, then fetch from API\ndevice = _isapi_devices.get(device_ip)\nif not device:\n    # Fetch credentials from API\n    try:\n        creds_url = f'http://localhost:{port}/api/v1/ptz/devices/{device_ip}/credentials'\n        async with aiohttp.ClientSession() as creds_session:\n            async with creds_session.get(creds_url, timeout=aiohttp.ClientTimeout(total=5)) as creds_resp:\n                if creds_resp.status == 200:\n                    creds_data = await creds_resp.json()\n                    if creds_data.get('success'):\n                        device = {\n                            'username': creds_data.get('username', 'admin'),\n                            'password': creds_data.get('password', ''),\n                            'port': creds_data.get('port', 80)\n                        }\n                        # Register for future requests\n                        _isapi_devices[device_ip] = device\n                        log.info('[ISAPI] Auto-registered device %s from credentials API', device_ip)\n    except Exception as e:\n        log.warning('[ISAPI] Failed to fetch credentials for %s: %s', device_ip, e)\n\nif not device:\n    device = {'username': 'admin', 'password': 'Nftw1357', 'port': device_port}  # fallback\n```\n\n注意：`port` 变量在文件开头定义（10280），直接使用。修改后不要过度开发。"}],"timestamp":1779306458875}}
